e=\"background-color:#104037\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brain-circuit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 5a3 3 0 1 0-5.997.125 4 4 0 0 0-2.526 5.77 4 4 0 0 0 .556 6.588A4 4 0 1 0 12 18Z\"></path><path d=\"M9 13a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3-4\"></path><path d=\"M6.003 5.125A3 3 0 0 0 6.401 6.5\"></path><path d=\"M3.477 10.896a4 4 0 0 1 .585-.396\"></path><path d=\"M6 18a4 4 0 0 1-1.967-.516\"></path><path d=\"M12 13h4\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h8\"></path><path d=\"M16 8V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2\"></path><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"13\" r=\".5\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"3\" r=\".5\"></circle><circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"21\" r=\".5\"></circle><circle cx=\"20\" cy=\"8\" r=\".5\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"service-card-title\">Behavioral Therapy</h3><p class=\"service-card-description\">Evidence-based behavior shaping with empathy and consistency.</p><a href=\"#\" class=\"service-card-link\">Learn more <span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"service-card\"><div class=\"service-card-icon-container\" style=\"background-color:#104037\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"service-card-title\">ABA Therapy</h3><p class=\"service-card-description\">Structured Applied Behavior Analysis personalised for every child.</p><a href=\"#\" class=\"service-card-link\">Learn more <span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"service-card\"><div class=\"service-card-icon-container\" style=\"background-color:#DE6A4D\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-graduation-cap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z\"></path><path d=\"M22 10v6\"></path><path d=\"M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"service-card-title\">Special Education</h3><p class=\"service-card-description\">Individualised learning plans aligned with academic milestones.</p><a href=\"#\" class=\"service-card-link\">Learn more <span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"service-card\"><div class=\"service-card-icon-container\" style=\"background-color:#104037\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-pulse\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path><path d=\"M3.22 13H9.5l.5-1 2 4.5 2-7 1.5 3.5h5.27\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"service-card-title\">Physiotherapy</h3><p class=\"service-card-description\">Strengthen posture, gait and gross-motor function safely.</p><a href=\"#\" class=\"service-card-link\">Learn more <span class=\"arrow\">→</span></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"conditions-section\"><div class=\"conditions-container\"><div class=\"conditions-sidebar\"><h4 class=\"conditions-label\">CONDITIONS WE SUPPORT</h4><h2 class=\"conditions-title\">A diagnosis is the beginning of a plan — not a verdict.</h2><p class=\"conditions-desc\">From first signs to lifelong independence, our clinical pathways are built around your child&#x27;s strengths.</p><a href=\"#all\" class=\"conditions-link\">All conditions <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"conditions-grid\"><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Autism Spectrum Disorder</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Multidisciplinary ASD pathways — assessment to long-term independence.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>ADHD</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Attention, focus and impulse-control programs that respect every learner.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Speech Delay</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Targeted speech therapy with measurable weekly milestones.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Developmental Delay</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Holistic catch-up plans across motor, speech, social and cognitive domains.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Learning Disabilities</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Dyslexia, dysgraphia, dyscalculia — academic success without stigma.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Cerebral Palsy</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Specialised PT/OT with adaptive technology and family coaching.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Down Syndrome</h3><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#DE6A4D\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><p>Lifelong skill-building with a strengths-based approach.</p></div><div class=\"condition-card\"><div class=\"condition-card-header\"><h3>Sensory Processing Disord